performance coatings performance colors and glass and pigments powders and oxides its performance coatings segment includes tile coating systems and porcelain enamel its manufacturers make products for various enduse markets the companys products fall into two general categories functional coatings which perform specific functions in the manufacturing processes and end products of its customers and color solutions which provide aesthetic and performance characteristics to its customers products its products are used in a range of product applications in markets including appliances automobiles building and renovation electronics household furnishings industrial products and packaging more from reuters » officers and directors peter t thomas chairman of the board president chief executive officer age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance benjamin schlater chief financial officer vice president age  bio  compensation   reuters mark hugo duesenberg vice president general counsel secretary age  bio  compensation   reuters jose tortajada vice president  human resources bio  compensation   reuters gregory e hyland lead independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters richard j hipple independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters david a lorber independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters andrew m ross independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters allen a spizzo independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service long ideas  seeking alphasign in  join nowgo»long ideaslargest acquisition to date a plus for starbuckssbux• today  pm • alt perspective• commentssap the right choices lead 