lazes stains decorating colors pigments inks polishing materials specialty dielectrics electronic glasses and other specialty coatings it operates through the following segments performance coatings performance colors and glass pigments powders and oxides the performance coatings segment refers to tile and porcelain enamel which offers products such as glazes digital inks and digital glaze coatings for use in a variety of ceramic tile applications the performance colors and glass segment offers color coatings and enamels for global glass industry such as automotive glass flat glass container glass and a range of industrial products applications the pigments powders and oxides segment covers paint plastics ceramics and concrete applications precious metal powders for conductive pastes and inks for a wide range of electronic applications and polishing materials for ophthalmic lenses auto finishes and display panels the company was founded by harry d cushman in  and is headquartered in mayfield heights oh see full profile analyst ratings sell under hold over buy number of ratings  full ratings credit suisse top  smallcap growth stocks aug   at  pm et on benzingacom benzingas top initiations aug   at  am et on benzingacom credit suisse sees ma opportunities on near horizon for ferro aug   at  am et on benzingacom competitors name chg  market cap guangshen railway co ltd adr  b wr grace  co  b omnova solutions inc  m cabot corp  b ppg industries inc  b competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by aks  sbux  dvax  x  bidu  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories th