cquisition dec   at  am et on accesswire ferro completes acquisition of cappelle pigments dec   at  am et on businesswire  bzx how these specialty chemicals stocks are faring  kraton ferro polyone and terravia nov   at  am et on pr newswire  prf correcting and replacing ferro schedules conference call for  thirdquarter results oct   at  am et on businesswire  bzx ferro corp ferro corp engages in the business of manufacturing specialty materials its products include frits porcelain and other glass enamels glazes stains decorating colors pigments inks polishing materials specialty dielectrics electronic glasses and other specialty coatings it operates through the following segments performance coatings performance colors and glass pigments powders and oxides the performance coatings segment refers to tile and porcelain enamel which offers products such as glazes digital inks and digital glaze coatings for use in a variety of ceramic tile applications the performance colors and glass segment offers color coatings and enamels for global glass industry such as automotive glass flat glass container glass and a range of industrial products applications the pigments powders and oxides segment covers paint plastics ceramics and concrete applications precious metal powders for conductive pastes and inks for a wide range of electronic applications and polishing materials for ophthalmic lenses auto finishes and display panels the company was founded by harry d cushman in  and is headquartered in mayfield heights oh see full profile analyst ratings sell under hold over buy number of ratings  full ratings credit suisse top  smallcap growth stocks aug   at  pm et on benzingacom benzingas top initiations aug   at  am et on benzingacom credit suisse sees ma opportunities on near horizon for ferro aug   at  am et on benzingacom competitors name chg  market cap guangshen railway co ltd adr  b wr grace  co  b omnova solutions inc  m cabot corp  b ppg industries inc  b competitor data p